{
  "stem": "18102.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did, quite extensively, and have had contact with the family of the-- Sugihara's sons and wife.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, in general, from a point of view of recognizing-- excuse me-- that here was a great man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think, directly, I did, because I, I was, as a child, of course, in a environment that was very much involved with Jewish life in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I grew up, of course, in Chicago once we settled here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents kept me very much involved with Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jewish life had a lot to do with the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't live in Jewish society from the 1940s on, through the present day, without having constant contact with the events that had happened during the Holocaust in Europe, and so I was immersed in this.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, I recited poetry at events commemorizing-- commemorating the uprising or the events in the ghetto, and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the only connection, in terms of Sugihara, was that he was the doorway to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't otherwise contemplate Sugihara, in response to your question, only that this was the avenue in which we, fortunately, were able to escape the, the consequences of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And only by virtue of my father's making all the right decisions along the way and Sugihara giving him this singular opportunity did I connect up the events.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So more important to me was the events in Poland, then in Russia and in Europe, as it relates to the Holocaust, than just that moment of opportunity that gave us the avenue to escape.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in more adult years than in my growing-up time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- I became involved in financial-- in the financial world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a consequence of that, I gave lectures in Japan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
